data.description: Situated on a corner lot, this 4 bed, 2 full bath home features almost 1,600sq ft of finished living space. The main level has 2 large living areas, a den / office, large kitchen, bedroom, and full bath. Upstairs you will find 3 good sized bedrooms and a 2nd full bath. Outside is a 2 car garage, and a fenced in front yard.
